{"tid":538749,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Intel：晶片漏洞更新檔有缺陷　用家不要安裝","createTime":"2018-01-24T02:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T15:19:49.000Z","uid":51620,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e1b6c4e790b51aa04f5909d55ba44f0ff04d6e35","tid":538749,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T02:09:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/01/23/intel-3/notebook/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2Fintel-3%2Fnotebook%2F&d=8V3KJs1r2MXkCAdtcbJ4fNWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=88451118\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/01/23/intel-3/notebook/</a><br />\n<br />\n早前，Intel CPU 被爆出「Meltdown」和「Spectre」兩個安全漏洞，讓全球電腦使用者無不提心吊膽。然而，針對上述兩個漏洞的安全更新，卻會造成自動重新啟動、系統不穩定，以及其他「不能預測」等問題。對此，Intel 發文警告用戶、合作夥伴，建議他們不要安裝最新的更新。<br />\n<br />\nIntel 執行副總裁 Neil Shenoy 在網誌先為電腦廠商與用戶造成的困擾致歉。今次受影響的是 Broadwell 與 Haswell 處理器的電腦與資料中心。文中表示更新檔會造成系統自動重新啟動，系統不穩定以及其他難以預測的結果，他們建議用戶、電腦製造商、雲端服務供應商不要進行更新。Intel 稱已經找出造成系統不穩的原因，將於本周末推出測試版更新。<br />\n<br />\n今次修補的是由 Speculative execution（推測執行）缺陷所引致的 3 個安全漏洞。早前通過微軟釋出的同類 AMD 系統更新亦出現過無法開機的問題。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://newsroom.intel.com/news/root-cause-of-reboot-issue-identified-updated-guidance-for-customers-and-partners/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.intel.com%2Fnews%2Froot-cause-of-reboot-issue-identified-updated-guidance-for-customers-and-partners%2F&d=8V3KJs1r2MXkCAdtcbJ4fNWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=fcecc091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newsroom.intel.com/news/root-cause-of-reboot-issue-identified-updated-guidance-for-customers-and-partners/</a>"},{"pid":"099df745e111c7b0209d4548057b73dad07b42c4","tid":538749,"uid":53105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T02:12:34.000Z","msg":"玩泥沙咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1204233fd8df5f58b36ea66a208cea5e08c072","tid":538749,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,